sequenceDiagram
    participant H as Human
    participant A as AI Agent (No Memory)
    
    Note over H,A: Customer Service Conversation
    
    H->>A: Review Jessica Norris's account<br/>for a credit limit increase
    activate A
    A->>A: Processes request<br/>Retrieves account data
    A-->>H: I've retrieved Jessica Norris's<br/>account details:<br/>• Credit limit: $5,000<br/>• Status: Active<br/>• Last payment: On time
    deactivate A
    
    Note over A: ⚠️ Memory lost - new request starts fresh
    
    H->>A: What was the last transaction<br/>on that account?
    activate A
    A->>A: ❌ Cannot resolve<br/>"that account"<br/>No context from previous message
    A-->>H: I apologize, but I don't have<br/>information about which account<br/>you're referring to. Could you<br/>please specify the account<br/>holder's name again?
    deactivate A
    
    Note over H,A: Without memory, the AI cannot resolve<br/>"that account" from the earlier message
